Package: GICHighDimension
Title: Generalized Information Criterion for Variable Selection Using Hopfield Network Optimization
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Yuchen", "Xiao", 
             email = "xiao.jack@utexas.edu", 
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2322-9660")),
      person("Stephen", "Walker",
             email = "s.g.walker@math.utexas.edu",
             role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides tools for variable selection in high-dimensional regression
    using the generalized information criterion (GIC) combined with Hopfield
    network optimization. Supports generalized linear models (GLMs), including
    normal and Poisson families. Performance-critical components are implemented
    in Julia with a user-friendly R interface via 'JuliaCall'.
